Page[511]=new Array(" ","@<br>Carefully consider and configure the appropriate output-off state, source, and compliance levels before connecting the Model 2651A to a device that can deliver energy (for example, other voltage sources, batteries, capacitors, solar cells, or other Model 2651A instruments ). Program recommended instrument settings before making connections to the device. Failure to consider the output-off state, source, and compliance levels may result in damage to the instrument or to the device under test (DUT).","Output-off states","15424.html");
